  <unit health="10" moveRange = "6" moves="2" determination="2" z="0.1">
    <name>Specialist</name>
    <action moveCost="1" actCost="1">
      <name>RPG</name>
      <targetAid>enemy</targetAid>
      <tip>Depite looking quite scary the main use of the rpg involves destruction of environment and supression as any determined unit will duck out of the blast wave</tip>

      <effect>
        <delivery>
